        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini; et anno ab incarnatione domini nostri Iesu Christi
                        millesimo octogesimo, mense aprilis, indictione .III. Ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3074">Gugliemus de Alno</persName>, cogitans huiusmodi
                        statum fragilem et caducum, et in nullo stabilitatem obtinere, nec hominem,
                        sine benefìciis et elemosinis, regnum coeleste posse acquirere, tandem
                        disposui et ordinavi partem mearum rationum, pro aeterna remuneratione, in
                        Dei servitio distribuere et offerre; ea propter notum volo esse cunctis Dei
                        fidelibus, nunc et in perpetuum existentibus, quod ego praefatus Guiglielmus
                        de Alno, ob amorem Dei et salutem animae nostrae, quam etiam pro salute
                        genitoris et genitricis nostrae, cum licentia et voluntate domini <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_magnificus" ref="#people/3002">Iordanis</persName>,
                            <rs key="#Vir_magnificus">magnifici</rs>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>, do, concedo et offero <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs><orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3000"> Sancti Laurentii levitae et martiris
                            Christi, qui dicitur ad Septimum</orgName>, non longe sito ab <placeName
                            key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000">Adverse</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbe</rs>, cui dominus <persName ref="#people/3004"
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank">Rainaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preaest, <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3021"
                            key="#Rivers #Landed_possessions #Forests #Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Churches"
                            >S. Nicolai, que est in Saone</orgName>, in <rs
                            key="#Village/castle_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/2363"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Village/castle_territory"><geogName
                                key="#Village/castle_territory" ref="#estates/3036"
                                >Calini</geogName></placeName>, cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs>, <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">cursibus
                            aquarum</rs>, que sunt in ipsa <placeName ref="#places/695"
                            key="#Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">Saone</placeName>,
                        cum omnibus suis pertinentiis cultis et incultis, <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvosis</rs> et insilvosis; et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras</rs>, et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">homines</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >molendina</rs>, et <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >cursus aquarum</rs>, quae sunt in loco <placeName ref="#places/4021"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Rivers #Landed_possessions #Forests #Mills #Coloni/tenants"
                            >Montanarii</placeName>, cum omnibus suis pertinentiis cultis et
                        incultis, <rs key="#Forests">silvosis</rs> et insilvosis; et <persName
                            key="#Priests"><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiterum</rs>, cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris cultis et incultis</rs>, silvosis et insilvosis, et sicut
                        tenuerunt <persName><name ref="Walpertus Hervenus">Gualberti
                            Herveno</name></persName>, Briptorum conditores, ut amodo in antea iam
                        dictum monasterium Sancti Laurentii prefata omnia in perpetuum teneat,
                        possideat et dominetur, libere et absolute ab omni censu, servitute et
                        dominatione, et ab omni serviti conditione. Et nullatenus mihi meisque
                        heredibus et successoribus, ac ulli humanae personae reservavimus potestatem
                        vel proprietatem aliquam; sed ab omni impedimento, libere et quiete,
                        prefatum monasterium omnia ut prelegitur possideat et dominetur, remota
                        etiam omni inquietudine vel molestatione cunctorumque mortalium personae.
                        Quod si quislibet hominum, magna vel privata persona, contra huius scripti
                        dominationem, concessionem et offertionem agere presumpserit, aut etiam
                        violator quocumque fieri tentaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri purissimi libras quinquagiuta</rs>, medietatem
                        camerae predicti domini principis et medietatem prefato monasterio. Et
                        soluta poena, huius nostrae donationis concessionis et offertionis scriptum
                        munitum, fìrmum ac stabile maneat in perpetuum. Ut autem hec nostra donatio,
                        concessio et oblatio firmiter credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur,
                        hoc scriptum manu nostra propria corroboravimus, atque subscriptos nobiles
                        testari, et te <persName key="#Writer" ref="#people/3005"
                            >Consolinum</persName> illa subscribere rogavimus, in predicto nostro
                        privilegio et subscripte propterea subsignavit. + Ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3074">Guilielmus de Alno</persName> qui supra. + Ego
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodulfus"
                        >Rodulfus</name></persName>. + Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Thomas">Thomas</name></persName>. + Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Aruinus de Sancto Midando">Horuindus de Sancto
                                Midando</name></persName> ferula nostrae trascripsi.</ab>
